Assignment 3 – CSS Selectors 

Website: https://www.amazon.in/ 

Tasks: 

- Search 'Laptop' using CSS ID → #twotabsearchtextbox. 
A-->  WebElement searchBox = driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("#twotabsearchtextbox"));
            searchBox.sendKeys("Laptop");

- Click search button using CSS Attribute → input[value='Go']. 
A--> WebElement searchButton = driver.findElement(By.cssSelector("input[value='Go']"));
            searchButton.click();

- Select the first product using nth-child CSS selector. 
A--> driver.findElement(By.cssSelector(".s-main-slot > div:nth-child(8) .puis-list-col-right a.a-link-normal.a-text-normal")).click();




